look like. If you remember we keep talking about

00:00:08.013 --> 00:00:12.728
get, keep and grow. But what does that exactly

00:00:12.728 --> 00:00:15.194
look like. What is it that you are doing. Well

00:00:15.194 --> 00:00:17.747
getting customers is just like it sounds. I need to

00:00:17.747 --> 00:00:20.478
acquire them and activate them. And if you

00:00:20.478 --> 00:00:24.025
remember Jersey Square team said, my primary

00:00:24.025 --> 00:00:27.532
channel will be our own company website. So,

00:00:27.532 --> 00:00:31.130
therefore probably my number one way of getting

00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:33.377
customers are Google AdWords. And you can see

00:00:33.377 --> 00:00:35.360
the little experiments that they ran here in the

00:00:35.360 --> 00:00:36.794
bottom and they are doing a whole bunch A/B

00:00:36.794 --> 00:00:39.426
testing and Google AdWord testing and Facebook

00:00:39.426 --> 00:00:42.015
testing. But they are trying to see whether that

00:00:42.015 --> 00:00:45.966
hypothesis about low cost acquisition is possible.

00:00:45.966 --> 00:00:47.903
