00:00:47.903 --> 00:00:51.367
YouTube and Twitter and they’re trying to see

00:00:51.367 --> 00:00:53.783
whether they can make their business viral by

00:00:53.783 --> 00:00:57.264
actually having customers who refer others. The

00:00:57.264 --> 00:01:00.732
key tenet of virality is can you get other people to

00:01:00.732 --> 00:01:03.337
do your marketing for free. And they are also

00:01:03.337 --> 00:01:05.631
